{"tid":1307251,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[幫手傳出去]重開: 香港聲援 行動資訊懶人包","createTime":"2019-07-11T13:04:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T17:32:11.000Z","uid":114,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"1506514b45dda31879624776285e2f3f432a0e98","tid":1307251,"uid":114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T13:04:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><code>我冇野講 我有權唔解鎖 我要搵律師 (背定律師電話) 我唔簽任何文件 我唔信任何警察 我要警誡記錄 我要食飯 飲水 毛氈 去廁所 我唔舒服要去醫院 我要睇你委任證同編號投訴你</code></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n借朋友acc出文<br />\n希望大家幫手傳出去<br />\n<br />\n多謝巴打提醒，所以我解返密先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港聲援 行動資訊懶人包<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/hkreinforce\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkreinforce&d=mly3UyGsD7RWnvW57yDWjgNVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=71ca27a4\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkreinforce</a><br />\n<br />\n將運動資訊整合做一個tg懶人包<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B4jdF56.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB4jdF56.png&h=d9fcc170&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n點選相應tag就可以睇到資訊，唔使再驚資訊亂哂唔知幾時去邊好<br />\n<br />\n有建議/ 問題/ 報料可以填表:<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/uKwsvbhzbBBky2mB8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FuKwsvbhzbBBky2mB8&d=mly3UyGsD7RWnvW57yDWjgNVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=9deaac93\" target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/uKwsvbhzbBBky2mB8</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OSUEBFd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOSUEBFd.png&h=ebef3f9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔使填個人資料，直接寫意見就得"},{"pid":"b9e66122556a2c7944698c1c60fd53afc4b19f25","tid":1307251,"uid":39752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T13:14:35.000Z","msg":"推埋俾 CD ROM 睇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b01f4b25161cf36a004d269993c6973261c486ab","tid":1307251,"uid":114,"like":0,"disl